{
  "stem": "13623.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The men will be working in an industrial area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they will let us stay together with our families.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These were rumors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe some of us wanted to believe them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because none of us had any idea what is in store for us up ahead.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were in-- in the ghetto only a short time, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] four to six weeks.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm not sure about that, but a few-- several weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Yiddish [NON-ENGLISH] started to run around from house to house with a new edict.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This time, it was everybody 14 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All males, 14 years and up, can only take what they can carry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they have to assemble in the local public school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We all [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] said goodbye from our mothers, and siblings, and grandparents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we did what we were asked to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We did assemble over in that public school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Some of us that were not as-- not too lucky-- there were a line of soldiers with fixed bayonets and some local civilian gentiles that were just standing there on both sides.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was a little foot bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had to cross a little foot bridge to get across to get to the school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Some of us, as we crossed that little foot bridge, between two lines of guards and local hooligans-- were-- they had sticks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And people started to get beaten and hit with the rifle butts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And where that stick fell, it could have-- it could fall just any place, on your head, on your back, on your legs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was no-- there was nobody that came to anybody's help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "If you fell down, you got hit even more so.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
